MCQ,Choices,Correct
What is the scientific study of life called?,a: Chemistry | b: Biology | c: Physics | d: Geology,b
Which theme in biology explains the unity and diversity of life?,a: Evolution | b: Energy processing | c: Cell theory | d: Genetics,a
What is the basic unit of life that processes hereditary information?,a: Atoms | b: Molecules | c: Cells | d: Tissues,c
At what levels of organization can biologists study life?,a: Only at the cellular level | b: Only at the molecular level | c: From molecular biology to evolution of populations | d: Only at the organism level,c
When did life on Earth emerge?,a: 1 billion years ago | b: 3.7 billion years ago | c: 5 billion years ago | d: 10 billion years ago,b
